fields.title: HFTS demystified
fields.subtitle: Talk from Alumni of IIT bombay on recent HFT comapnies
fields.description: HFTS Demystified is an illuminating workshop featuring an insightful talk by an esteemed alumnus of IIT Bombay. Focused on recent developments in High-Frequency Trading (HFT) companies, this workshop aims to unravel the intricacies of HFT and provides valuable insights on securing employment in this dynamic sector. Attendees will gain a comprehensive understanding of HFT companies and practical guidance on navigating the job landscape within this domain.

fields.title: CP 101 Workshop

fields.description: CP 101 is an engaging workshop designed to provide a foundational understanding of Competitive Programming (CP). Join us to explore the fundamentals and enhance your skills in tackling CP questions.

fields.title: Intro to Cyber Security

fields.description: The 'Intro to Cybersecurity Workshop' is an informative session designed to cover the essentials of cybersecurity. Join us to gain a comprehensive understanding of cybersecurity and learn the foundational elements crucial for mastering this dynamic and vital domain.

By offering personalized mentorship and valuable resources, the program aims to equip individuals with the knowledge and skills necessary to excel in the competitive programming domain.
